title: Stafford scores twice, Jets beat Wild 5-4

Trevor Hagan Stafford scores twice, Jets beat Wild 5-4 
Winnipeg Jets' Andrew Ladd (16) scores as he fires the puck past Minnesota Wild's Ryan Suter (20), Jets' Bryan Little (18), Wild's Jared Spurgeon (46) and goaltender Darcy Kuemper (35) during first-period NHL hockey game action in Winnipeg, Manitoba, Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015. Winnipeg Jets' Bryan Little (18) scores against Minnesota Wild goaltender Darcy Kuemper (35) as he is checked by Jason Pominville (29) with Ryan Suter (20) in front of the net during first-period NHL hockey game action in Winnipeg, Manitoba, Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015. (Trevor Hagan/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT Trevor Hagan Stafford scores twice, Jets beat Wild 5-4 
Winnipeg Jets' Toby Enstrom (39) celebrates with Andrew Ladd (16) after Ladd scored against the Minnesota Wild during first period NHL hockey action in Winnipeg, Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015. (Trevor Hagan/The Canadian Press via AP) Trevor Hagan Stafford scores twice, Jets beat Wild 5-4 
Winnipeg Jets' Andrew Copp (9) gets tangled up with Minnesota Wild goaltender Darcy Kuemper (35) during first period NHL hockey action in Winnipeg, Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015. (Trevor Hagan/The Canadian Press via AP) Trevor Hagan Stafford scores twice, Jets beat Wild 5-4 
Winnipeg Jets' Jacob Trouba (8) stops a puck from sliding over the goal line after it got past goaltender Michael Hutchinson (34) while playing against the Minnesota Wild during first-period NHL hockey game action in Winnipeg, Manitoba, Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015. (Trevor Hagan/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT Posted: Sunday, October 25, 2015 9:28 pm
